        <br>in order to prevent waste.<p>
    <div class="col my-5"> <!--- navbar links --->

      <div class="home-slogan-box my-5"> <!--- left side text intro --->
        <h2 class="home-slogan">Fight hunger
        <br>fight food
        <br>waste<h2>
      </div>

      <div class="home-intro">
        <p>We connect <b>food producers</b>
        <br>with <b>homeless shelters</b>
        <br>to provide <b>food</b> to people in <b>need</b>
        <br>in order to <b>prevent waste.</b><p>
