        <p class="mb-0 pb-4" id="info-bar-txt">
          Food waste generates a resounding loss of
          <br>940 billion dollars per year, affecting not
          <br>only the less priviliged but also Brazil’s economy
        </p>
        <%= cl_image_tag "https://res.cloudinary.com/dnczymjwi/image/upload/w_1000,ar_16:9,c_fill,g_auto,e_sharpen/v1637771779/ex-animo/img2-home-page_xubldb.png",:height=>300, :width=>700 %>

    <div class="info-img"> <!--- info img --->
      <%= image_tag "https://source.unsplash.com/random", style: 'height:500px;width:100%;'%>
    </div>

